data.description: Welcome to one of the LARGEST and most PRIVATE backyards you'll find in the Firebridge subdivision. This cute 3 bed/2 bath home sits in a Cul-de-sac and has been very well kept by the owners. Super quiet street, modern concrete counter top, finished deck overlooking the HUGE backyard that is surrounded by nature, not by other properties. The Subdivision's own boat/RV storage is literally next door, giving you easy access to them 24/7. There is a powered shed, a storage unit and and a beautiful pergola, inviting you to spend many hours outdoors with friends and family. The kitchen and living room are seamlessly connected and of course, the location is everything you can ask. Chapin schools and amenities are so close you won't be spending much time driving around. Make an appointment today because tomorrow will be too late.
